{"lastModified":1751641526442,"uri":"c::9870482971::vessel::d5cc2450-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy\n\nThe 22.8m/74'10\" sail yacht 'Paulena' by shipyard Sangermani offers flexible accommodation\nfor up to 7 guests in 4 cabins.\n\nWith the Sangermani \"Paulena,\" you can discover the charm of cruising on one of the most\nbeautiful classic yachts in the Mediterranean. Masterfully conducted by a professional crew, you will appreciate the comfort of sailing on a Classic Yawl on a dream vacation for family and friends.\n\nDesigned in 1964 and launched in 1966 by the famous Ligurian shipyard Sangermani, she has\nalways been kept in perfect condition and in accordance with the initial design, Paulena is a\nvessel of great class and unmistakable style.\n\nThe interior consists of a spacious and bright saloon, with a dining table that can comfortably\naccommodate up to ten guests. Aft is the owner's quarters consisting of a large full-width cabin with two French beds, shower room and sink, a toilet room with sink and shower, and a large single cabin. Toward the bow we find two guest cabins both with twin beds served by a large bathroom with sink, shower and toilet.\n\nThe crew quarters and the galley are located forward in separate rooms with separate entrances.\n\nAll rooms are equipped with air conditioning (cold/hot) that can be individually controlled for\nmaximum comfort. The boat is equipped with TV system with VCR, internal and external stereo, PC with Internet connection and satellite telephone. Snorkeling and sport fishing equipment complete the amenities.\n\nThanks to the Captain’s passion for good food, Paulena allows to offer the most demanding\nguest a wide choice of dishes that, together with the tasting of excellent wines, will make the\nmoments spent on board unforgettable.\n","blueprint":{"name":"PAULENA","images":["/media/media::image::c::9870482971::vessel::d5cc2450-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb72